# 📊 Accounts Receivable (AR) Analysis Using SQL

## Project Overview

This project analyzes Accounts Receivable (AR) data using SQL. The objective is to identify payment trends, outstanding balances, customer payment behavior, and key financial metrics that are commonly used by Finance, AR, and Business Intelligence teams.

### Skills Demonstrated

* SQL DDL (CREATE TABLE)
* SQL DML (INSERT)
* Data Aggregation
* Filtering & Sorting
* CASE Statements
* Common Table Expressions (CTEs)
* Window Functions
* Ranking Functions
* Business KPI Reporting
* Accounts Receivable Analysis

---

# Dataset Creation

## Create Table

```sql
CREATE TABLE AR_Analysis (
    InvoiceID INTEGER,
    Customer_Name VARCHAR(40),
    Invoice_Date DATE,
    Inv_Amount INTEGER,
    Regions VARCHAR(40),
    Country VARCHAR(40),
    Due_Date DATE,
    Payment_Status VARCHAR(40)
);
```

